  "status": "Draft",
  "summary": "This proposal recommends an extension of [ERC-721](./eip-721.md) to allow for collateralization using a list of [ERC-20](./eip-20.md) based tokens. The proprietor of this ERC collection could hold both the native coin and [ERC-20](./eip-20.md) based tokens, with the `ownerOf` tokenId being able to unlock the associated portion of the underlying [ERC-20](./eip-20.md) balance.",
  "title": "Collateralized NFT"
